claim.claim-text:
An information processing apparatus (20), comprising:
a management unit (24) configured to:
receive first video data, first application data and a first application information table, wherein the first application information table defines a life cycle of the first application data broadcast with the first video data, and the first application data includes information indicating a location of a second application information table in a network;
manage the first application data based on the first application information table; and
manage the first application data based on the second application information table;
wherein the second application information table is equivalent to the first application information table in that the first application data can be managed using both the first application information table or the second application information table.

An information processing method comprising:
receiving first video data, first application data and a first application information table, wherein the first application information table defines a life cycle of the first application data broadcast with the first video data, and the first application data includes information indicating a location of a second application information table in a network;
managing the first application data based on the first application information table; and
managing the first application data based on the second application information table;
wherein the second application information table is equivalent to the first application information table in that the first application data can be managed using both the first application information table or the second application information table.
